    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a razor-sharp throttle response and a screaming 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanically flawless, the chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement and a complete cooling system overhaul with OE components. The exterior retains its factory-spec paint depth with no signs of oxidation or swirl marks, while the interior leather maintains its original matte finish. For the collector seeking a high-revving, analog masterpiece, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of M-Division engineering in pristine, turn-key condition.",
