    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolutely flawless 2018 BMW M5 in Marina Bay Blue Metallic. This vehicle is in true showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint is deep and lustrous, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. The 20-inch M-Double spoke wheels are pristine, wrapped in brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. Inside, the Silverstone Full Merino Leather remains supple and unmarked; the bolsters show no signs of wear, and the cabin still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every piece of carbon fiber trim is scratch-free, and the electronics function perfectly. Mechanically, this M5 is beyond reproach. It has a complete, documented service history solely through BMW certified technicians, with the most recent major service just completed. It has never seen a track, never seen rain, and has been driven with the utmost care. Included are both original keys, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a high-performance legend that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 44900.0,
