      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-standard condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects a commitment to meticulous maintenance, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, factory-fresh interior. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of uncompromising quality and mechanical integrity. We invite discerning collectors to experience a vehicle that defies its age and surpasses all expectations.",
