    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a pinnacle of JDM engineering. This example retains its factory-original 2JZ-GTE sequential twin-turbocharged inline-six, mated to the legendary Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is beyond reproach, featuring a pristine Torsen limited-slip differential and untouched factory suspension geometry. All VIN tags are present on the original body panels, confirming an accident-free history. The engine bay is a time capsule, showing zero oxidation on the aluminum castings and no heat-cycling fatigue on the vacuum lines. Performance remains crisp, with the turbos spooling linearly and holding peak boost without deviation. This is a concours-level specimen for the discerning collector who demands mechanical purity.",
